---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Start With Free Resources - Build Your Wellbeing Leadership | Craig Fearn"
  description="Access free resources, then choose your investment level. From free wellbeing frameworks to £25K+ strategic transformations. Start your wellbeing leadership journey today.">

  <!-- Hero Section with Value Ladder Introduction -->
  <section class="section-padding-hero bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-indigo-900 text-white">
    <div class="container max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-hero mb-6">
          Choose Your Investment Level
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          From free frameworks that work, to strategic transformations that reshape organisations.
          Start where you are. Scale when you're ready.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-h2 mb-6 text-center">The Wellbeing Leadership Path</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-green-300">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">FREE</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90">Start Here</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-yellow-300">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">£47</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90">Go Deeper</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-orange-300">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">£997</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90">Transform</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-red-300">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">£25K+</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90">Scale Impact</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Ladder Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-h1 text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Explore Our Services. Start Your Conversation.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Every leader's wellbeing journey is different. Discover our range of services and let's discuss what's right for your situation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Value Ladder -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- FREE Tier -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-green-50 to-white border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl p-8 relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-green-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">START HERE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">FREE</div>
            <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Wellbeing Leadership Foundations</h3>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Weekly wellbeing leadership insights email</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Free Board Wellbeing Readiness Assessment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>"5 Questions Every Board Must Answer" guide</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Access to Craig's LinkedIn content library</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Monthly wellbeing governance webinars</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <Button href="#email-signup" variant="primary" class="w-full bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700">
            Get Free Resources
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- £47 Tier -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-50 to-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-2xl p-8 relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-yellow-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">MOST POPULAR</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-600 mb-2">£47</div>
            <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Board Wellbeing Audit Kit</h3>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Complete board assessment framework</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>47-point governance readiness checklist</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>ROI calculator for wellbeing initiatives</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Board presentation templates</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>60-minute video masterclass with Craig</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Implementation timeline planner</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="w-full bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700">
            Get the Kit
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- £997 Tier -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-50 to-white border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-2xl p-8 relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-orange-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">ACCELERATED</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">£997</div>
            <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Strategic Wellbeing Assessment</h3>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Complete AI-enhanced organisational audit</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>90-minute strategy session with Craig</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Bespoke improvement roadmap</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Board-ready presentation deck</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>3 months email support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Implementation toolkit</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="w-full bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700">
            Book Assessment
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- £25K+ Tier -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-red-50 to-white border-2 border-red-200 rounded-2xl p-8 relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-red-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">TRANSFORMATION</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">£25K+</div>
            <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Strategic Transformation Partnership</h3>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>12-month strategic partnership</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Monthly board advisory sessions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Executive team coaching programme</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Complete wellbeing transformation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Direct access to Craig via WhatsApp</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Guaranteed ROI measurement & reporting</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700">
            Apply for Partnership
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Approach Works -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-h1 text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Why Smart Leaders Start Free
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          I was once the director who didn't know if our wellbeing strategy was working. That uncomfortable truth led to frameworks now used by FTSE companies and NHS Trusts.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Test Before You Invest</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">See if my approach resonates with your leadership style before committing significant resources.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Immediate Value</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Every tier delivers actionable insights you can implement immediately, regardless of budget.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Proven at Scale</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">The same frameworks work whether you're a startup founder or FTSE 100 board member.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Email Signup Section -->
  <section id="email-signup" class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 via-indigo-900 to-purple-900 text-white">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-h1 mb-6">
        Start Your Journey Today
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Join 2,500+ leaders who receive practical wellbeing governance insights every Tuesday at 7am.
        No fluff. No theory. Just actionable frameworks you can implement this week.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <form class="space-y-4">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <label class="sr-only" for="firstName">First Name</label>
            <input
              id="firstName"
              name="firstName"
              type="text"
              placeholder="First Name"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/20 border border-white/30 text-white placeholder-white/70 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
              required
              aria-label="First Name"
            />
            <label class="sr-only" for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input
              id="email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              placeholder="Email Address"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/20 border border-white/30 text-white placeholder-white/70 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
              required
              aria-label="Email Address"
            />
          </div>
          <label class="sr-only" for="challenge">What's your biggest wellbeing challenge?</label>
          <select id="challenge" name="challenge" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/20 border border-white/30 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400" aria-label="Select your biggest wellbeing challenge">
            <option value="" disabled selected class="text-gray-900">What's your biggest wellbeing challenge?</option>
            <option value="board-buy-in" class="text-gray-900">Getting board buy-in for wellbeing initiatives</option>
            <option value="roi-measurement" class="text-gray-900">Measuring ROI of wellbeing programmes</option>
            <option value="strategic-integration" class="text-gray-900">Integrating wellbeing into business strategy</option>
            <option value="compliance-governance" class="text-gray-900">ISO 45003 compliance and governance</option>
            <option value="leadership-development" class="text-gray-900">Developing wellbeing leadership skills</option>
          </select>
          <Button type="submit" variant="white" size="large" class="w-full shadow-lg">
            Send Me Free Resources
          </Button>
        </form>

        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-6">
          Unsubscribe anytime. I respect your inbox and your time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social Proof & Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="text-h1 text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Join 2,500+ Leaders Building Better Workplaces
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        From NHS Trust directors to FTSE 100 board members, leaders choose Craig's frameworks because they work at every scale.
      </p>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">2,500+</div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Weekly Email Readers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Leaders who implement Craig's frameworks every Tuesday</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100+</div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Organisations Transformed</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">FTSE companies and NHS Trusts using Craig's methodology</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">17+</div>
          <h3 class="text-h3 text-gray-900 mb-4">Years Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Fellow-level expertise in wellbeing governance</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-blue-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-12">
        <h3 class="text-h2 mb-6">
          Ready to Build Your Wellbeing Leadership?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Choose your starting point. Every tier delivers immediate value, whether you're just beginning or ready for full transformation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="#email-signup" variant="white" size="large" class="shadow-lg">
            Start Free
          </Button>
          <Button href="/contact" variant="ghost" size="large" class="!bg-transparent !border-2 !border-white !text-white hover:!bg-white hover:!text-slate-900">
            Book a Call
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

